ed states the castings segment manufactures and sells steel investment castings and metal injection molding mim parts the companys design and manufacturing operations are located in the united states the company primarily offers products in three industry product categories rifles pistols and revolvers the companys firearms are sold through independent wholesale distributors principally to the commercial sporting market the company manufactures firearm products under the ruger name the company also manufactures and sells accessories and replacement parts for its firearms receive news  ratings via email  enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts ratings with marketbeatcoms free daily email newsletter leave a reply cancel reply your email address will not be published required fields are marked comment name  email  website more news a statement released earlier today by rbc capital markets about asanko gold tseakg bumps down the target price to  stating a potential upside of  au optronics nyseauo has been downgraded from neutral to underperform in a report by bank of america merrill lynch today bank of america merrill lynch has a statement released earlier today by cowen about allegiant travel ndaqalgt bumps down the target price to  stating a potential upside of  a statement released earlier today by canaccord genuity about agnico eagle mines tseaem ups the target price to  having a price of  agnico a statement released earlier today by fbr amp co about owens corning nyseoc raises the target price to  boasting a price of  owens rbc capital markets disclosed ameriprise financial inc nyseamp upping its target price to  earlier today rbc capital markets bumped up the a statement released earlier today by scotia capital about bce inc tsebce bumps down the target price to  stating a potential upside of  buffalo wild wings ndaqbwld target price lowered to  issued a report today by maxim group yesterday buffalo wild wi