 a free replacement lock for more information call sturm ruger  company inc tollfree at   between  am and  pm et monday through friday or visit rugers website at wwwruger firearmscom consumers should always be sure to obey all laws and follow appropriate safety procedures when storing their firearms consumers are reminded to make sure their unloaded gun is secure until the new replacement lock is received the us consumer product safety commission is charged with protecting the public from unreasonable risks of injury or death associated with the use of thousands of types of consumer products under the agency’s jurisdiction deaths injuries and property damage from consumer product incidents cost the nation more than  trillion annually cpsc is committed to protecting consumers and families from products that pose a fire electrical chemical or mechanical hazard cpscs work to help ensure the safety of consumer products  such as toys cribs power tools cigarette lighters and household chemicals – contributed to a decline in the rate of deaths and injuries associated with consumer products over the past  years federal law bars any person from selling products subject to a publiclyannounced voluntary recall by a manufacturer or a mandatory recall ordered by the commission to report a dangerous product or a productrelated injury go online to wwwsaferproductsgov or call cpscs hotline at  or teletypewriter at  for the hearing impaired consumers can obtain news release and recall information at wwwcpscgov on twitter uscpsc or by subscribing to cpscs free email newsletters media contact please use the below phone number for all media requests phone   spanish   view cpsc contacts for specific areas of expertise related recalls irover recalls selfbalancing scootershoverboards due to fire hazard polaris recalls sportsman  allterrain vehicles due to fuel leak fire hazards corbeau usa recalls camlock seat harness belts due to fall and projectile hazards polaris recalls rzr  and rzr s  recreational offhighway vehicles due to crash and injury hazards recall alert recall alert triggertech recalls crossbow and rifletriggers due to injury hazard search product safety reports search product safety reports on saferproductsgov find more about government recalls recallsgov find recalls from around the world global recall portal × you are about to leave the us consumer product safety commission cpsc public website the link you selected is for a destination outside of the federal government cpsc does not control this external site or its privacy policy and cannot attest to the accuracy of the information it contains you may wish to review the privacy policy of the external site as its information collection practices may differ from ours linking to this external site does not constitute an endorsement of the site or the information it contains by cpsc or any of its employees click ok if you wish to continue to the website otherwise click cancel to return to our site ok cancel sturm ruger  co  wikipedia sturm ruger  co from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from sturm ruger  co inc jump to navigation search ruger redirects here for other uses see ruger disambiguation sturm ruger  company inc type public traded as nyse rgr sp  component industry firearms founded   years ago  founder william b ruger and alexander mccormick sturm headquarters southport connecticut united states area served worldwide key people c michael jacobi chairman christopher j killoy president and chief executive officer thomas a dineen vice president and treasurer and chief financial officer products revolvers pistols rifles shotguns revenue  million  number of employees   website wwwrugercom sturm ruger  co inc better known by the shortened name ruger is an american firearm manufacturing company based in southport connecticut with production facilities also in newport new hampshire mayodan north carolina and prescott arizona the company was founded in  by alexander mccormick sturm and william b ruger and has been publicly traded since  ruger produces boltaction semiautomatic and singleshot rifles shotguns semiautomatic pistols and single and doubleaction revolvers according to the atf statistics for  ruger is currently americas largest firearm manufacturer as well as the second largest pistolrevolver manufacturer behind smith  wesson and rifle manufacturer behind remington in the usa contents  history  facilities  statistics  products  boltaction rifles  singleshot rifles  autoloading rifles  leveraction rifles  shotguns  centerfire pistols  rimfire pistols  doubleaction revolvers  singleaction revolvers  ruger and the usa shooting team  see also  bibliography  references  external links historyedit rugers mk ii  target pistol sturm ruger  company was founded by william b ruger and alexander mccormick sturm in  in a small rented machine shop in southport connecticut just prior to their partnership bill ruger had successfully duplicated two japanese baby nambu pistols in his garage from a captured nambu that he acquired from a returning marine at the close of world war ii when it came to designing their first semiauto pistol ruger decided to incorporate the looks of the german mm luger and the american colt woodsman into their first commercially produced  caliber pistol see ruger standard which became so successful that it launched the entire company ruger is a dominant manufacturer in the  lr rimfire rifle market in the us due primarily to the sales of its ruger  semiautomatic rifle the  is very popular due to being relatively inexpensive and of good quality as a result a wealth of aftermarket accessories and parts were made available for it which has further increased its popularity the availability and variety of aftermarket parts makes it possible to build a  using only these parts most of which are marketed to target shooters and hunters ruger similarly dominates the  rimfire semiautomatic pistol market with the ruger mk ii and ruger mk iii descendants of the ruger standard pistol like the  the mkii is supported with a wide variety of aftermarket accessories the  is similar to the ruger standard family of pistols but features a different grip angle that of the colt  as opposed to that of a luger utilized in the ruger standard ruger casting has plants in newport new hampshire and prescott arizona making ferrous ductile iron and commercial titanium castings ruger golf makes steel and titanium castings for golf clubs made by a number of different brands sturm ruger stock has been publicly traded since  and became a new york stock exchange company in  nysergr after alex sturm’s death in  william b ruger continued to direct the company until his death in  from  through  ruger manufactured over  million firearms and currently offers models for hunting target shooting selfdefense collecting and law enforcement facilitiesedit sturm ruger  co is headquartered in southport connecticut and maintains manufacturing facilities in newport new hampshire prescott arizona and mayodan north carolina rugers subsidiaries are ruger precision metals llc in earth city missouri pine tree castings in newport new hampshire and ruger sportswear  accessories in mayodan north carolina statisticsedit of the total  makers of civilian firearms operating in the united states from – ruger led the industry with  million firearms produced within the period ruger was ranked the number one us firearms manufacturer from – in  ruger manufactured  firearms as their promotion the million gun challenge to benefit the nra played a significant role in the company maintaining its top us manufacturer status the company has set a new goal of  million firearms produced per year from  to  ruger was the topseller of handguns productsedit ruger breaks down their products into nine categories boltaction rifles singleshot rifles autoloading rifles leveraction rifles shotguns centerfire pistols rimfire pistols doubleaction revolvers and singleaction revolvers boltaction riflesedit ruger m mark ii stainless bolt action in  hawkeye m guide gun hawkeye african gunsite scout rifle model  american rifle american rimfire ruger precision rifle singleshot riflesedit no  no  discontinued autoloading riflesedit ruger  stainless with an aftermarket butler creek folding stock and a truglo red dot sight model  discontinued   discontinued sr mini xgi not produced development halted police carbine discontinued deerfield carbine discontinued ar sr discontinued sr leveraction riflesedit model    and  discontinued shotgunsedit red label discontinued gold label discontinued centerfire pistolsedit ruger p hawkeye discontinued p series discontinued sr series sr lcp lcp ii lc lc lcs ruger american pistol e rimfire pistolsedit ruger mk standard mk i discontinued mk ii discontinued mk iii   discontinued mk iv sr  charger doubleaction revolversedit the first variation of the ruger lcr  special with laser grips securitysixservicesixspeedsix discontinued redhawk gp sp super redhawk super redhawk alaskan lcr singleaction revolversedit stainless new model super blackhawk and redhawk bearcat singlesix blackhawk super blackhawk vaquero old army discontinued ruger and the usa shooting teamedit sturm ruger  co has a history of assisting the usa shooting team in direct funds contribution and by creating distributor exclusive models through talo distributors inc see alsoedit list of modern armament manufacturers talo distributors bibliographyedit wilson r l  ruger  his guns a history of the man the company and their firearms isbn   referencesedit  ruger ruger board of directors  c michael jacobi retrieved march     ruger ruger board of directors  christopher j killoy retrieved may     ruger ruger board of directors  thomas a dineen retrieved march     a b corporate report pdf february     corporate news july     batfe annual firearms manufacturing and export report    batfe annual firearms manufacturing and export report   can you guess the 