otification join our mailing list sturm ruger  co  wikipedia sturm ruger  co from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search ruger redirects here for other uses see ruger disambiguation sturm ruger  company inc type public traded as nyse rgr sp  component industry firearms founded   years ago  founder william b ruger and alexander mccormick sturm headquarters southport connecticut united states area served worldwide key people c michael jacobi chairman christopher j killoy president and chief executive officer thomas a dineen vice president and treasurer and chief financial officer products revolvers pistols rifles shotguns revenue  million  number of employees   website wwwrugercom sturm ruger  co inc better known by the shortened name ruger is an american firearm manufacturing company based in southport connecticut with production facilities also in newport new hampshire mayodan north carolina and prescott arizona the company was founded in  by alexander mccormick sturm and william b ruger and has been publicly traded since  ruger produces boltaction semiautomatic and singleshot rifles shotguns semiautomatic pistols and single and doubleaction revolvers according to the atf statistics for  ruger is currently americas largest firearm manufacturer as well as the second largest pistolrevolver manufacturer behind smith  wesson and rifle manufacturer behind remington in the usa contents  history  facilities  statistics  products  boltaction rifles  singleshot rifles  autoloading rifles  leveraction rifles  shotguns  centerfire pistols  rimfire pistols  doubleaction revolvers  singleaction revolvers  ruger and the usa shooting team  see also  bibliography  references  external links historyedit rugers mk ii  target pistol sturm ruger  company was founded by william b ruger and alexander mccormick sturm in  in a small rented machine shop in southport connecticut just prior to their partnership bill ruger had successfully duplicated two japanese baby nambu pistols in his garage from a captured nambu that he acquired from a returning marine at the close of world war ii when it came to designing their first semiauto pistol ruger decided to incorporate the looks of the german mm luger and the american colt woodsman into their first commercially produced  caliber pistol see ruger standard which became so successful that it launched the entire company ruger is a dominant manufacturer in the  lr rimfire rifle market in the us due primarily to the sales of its ruger  semiautomatic rifle the  is very popular due to being relatively inexpensive and of good quality as a result a wealth of aftermarket accessories and parts were made available for it which has further increased its popularity the availability and variety of aftermarket parts makes it possible to build a  using only these parts most of which are marketed to target shooters and hunters ruger similarly dominates the  rimfire semiautomatic pistol market with the ruger mk ii and ruger mk iii descendants of the ruger standard pistol like the  the mkii is supported with a wide variety of aftermarket accessories the  is similar to the ruger standard family of pistols but features a different grip angle that of the colt  as opposed to that of a luger utilized in the ruger standard ruger casting has plants in newport new hampshire and prescott arizona making ferrous ductile iron and commercial titanium castings ruger golf makes steel and titanium castings for golf clubs made by a number of different brands sturm ruger stock has been publicly traded since  and became a new york stock exchange company in  nysergr after alex sturm’s death in  william b ruger continued to direct the company until his death in  from  through  ruger manufactured over  million firearms and currently offers models for hunting target shooting selfdefense collecting and law enforcement facilitiesedit sturm ruger  co is headquartered in southport connecticut and maintains manufacturing facilities in newport new hampshire prescott arizona and mayodan north carolina rugers subsidiaries are ruger precision metals llc in earth city missouri pine tree castings in newport new hampshire and ruger sportswear  accessories in mayodan north carolina statisticsedit of the total  makers of civilian firearms operating in the united states from – ruger led the industry with  million firearms produced within the period ruger was ranked the number one us firearms manufacturer from – in  ruger manufactured  firearms as their promotion the million gun challenge to benefit the nra played a significant role in the company maintaining its top us manufacturer status the company has set a new goal of  million firearms produced per year from  to  ruger was the topseller of handguns productsedit ruger breaks down their products into nine categories boltaction rifles singleshot rifles autoloading rifles leveraction rifles shotguns centerfire pistols rimfire pistols doubleaction revolvers and singleaction revolvers boltaction riflesedit ruger m mark ii stainless bolt action in  hawkeye m guide gun hawkeye african gunsite scout rifle model  american rifle american rimfire ruger precision rifle singleshot riflesedit no  no  discontinued autoloading riflesedit ruger  stainless with an aftermarket butler creek folding stock and a truglo red dot sight model  discontinued   discontinued sr mini xgi not produced development halted police carbine discontinued deerfield carbine discontinued ar sr discontinued sr leveraction riflesedit model    and  discontinued shotgunsedit red label discontinued gold label discontinued centerfire pistolsedit ruger p hawkeye discontinued p series discontinued sr series sr lcp lcp ii lc lc lcs ruger american pistol e rimfire pistolsedit ruger mk standard mk i discontinued mk ii discontinued mk iii   discontinued mk iv sr  charger doubleaction revolversedit the first variation of the ruger lcr  special with laser grips securitysixservicesixspeedsix discontinued redhawk gp sp super redhawk super redhawk alaskan lcr singleaction revolversedit stainless new model super blackhawk and redhawk bearcat singlesix blackhawk super blackhawk vaquero old army discontinued ruger and the usa shooting teamedit sturm ruger  co has a history of assisting the usa shooting team in direct funds contribution and by creating distributor exclusive models through talo distributors inc see alsoedit list of modern armament manufacturers talo distributors bibliographyedit wilson r l  ruger  his guns a history of the man the company and their firearms isbn   referencesedit  ruger ruger board of directors  c michael jacobi retrieved march     ruger ruger board of directors  christopher j killoy retrieved may     ruger ruger board of directors  thomas a dineen retrieved march     a b corporate report pdf february     corporate news july     batfe annual firearms manufacturing and export report    batfe annual firearms manufacturing and export report   can you guess the biggest gunmaker in the us  a b wilson  p   a b house james e  july  customize the ruger  iola wisconsin fw media pp – isbn    garrison kerry  march  getting to know the ruger  everything you need to know to shoot clean maintain and modify your ruger  kerry garrison pp – isbn    sweeney patrick  december  the gun digest book of ruger pistols and revolvers iola wisconsin gun digest books p  isbn x   phd gregg lee carter  may  guns in american society an encyclopedia of history politics culture and the law  volumes abcclio p  isbn    httpwwwrugercomcorporatedirectoryhtml  guns at a glance  of all firearms made in america come from these  companies the blaze march     us firearms industry today shooting industry    httprugercommicrosmillionindexhtml  us firearms industry today shooting industry    gallery of guns  shooting times  gun reviews  ruger raffle for usa shooting team nssf  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to sturm ruger  company inc sturm ruger  co official site 